name beamertheme-pure-minimalistic
category Package
revision 56934
shortdesc A minimalistic presentation theme for LaTeX Beamer
longdesc The main features of this minimalistic Beamer theme are: Easily
longdesc use own logos. Customizable. Looks good in a 4:3 and 16:9
longdesc aspect ratio, without the need to change anything. Provides an
longdesc environment for vertically-spaced items. Provides light and
longdesc dark mode. Is designed to be purely minimalistic without any
longdesc distractions.
